Module ntnu.team1
Package ntnu.team1

Class MainRegister

  • java.lang.Object
    • ntnu.team1.MainRegister
  • public class MainRegister
extends java.lang.Object
    This is is the main register of the whole app It keeps track of all categories and tasks by storing them in a HashMap and an ArrayList The Mainregister also allows for adding tasks and adding categories to the registers It also handles saving and reading from file, it also sorts the registers
